onah Blank|author2=Christopher Clary|author3=Brian Nichiporuk|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=sSZRBgAAQBAJ&pg=PA19|title=Drivers of Long-Term insecurity and Instability in Pakistan: Urbanization|date=30 October 2014|publisher=Rand Corporation|isbn=978-0-8330-8751-5|p=19|ref={{sfnref|Jonah Blank|Christopher Clary|Brian Nichiporuk|2014}}}}\n* {{citation |author=Stephen P. Cohen|title=The Idea of Pakistan|year=2004|publisher=[[Brookings Institution Press]]|isbn=978-0-8157-9761-6|p=202|ref={{sfnref|Stephen P. Cohen|2004}}}}\n* {{citation |author=Q. Ashton Acton|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=DrCxJ4F8f0cC&pg=PT278|title=Issues in National, Regional, and Environmental Health and Medicine: 2013 Edition|date=1 May 2013|publisher=ScholarlyEditions|isbn=978-1-4901-1294-7|p=278|ref={{sfnref|Issues in National, Regional, and Environmental Health and Medicine|2013}}}}\n* {{citation |author=Q. Ashton Acton|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=CwtnpymlSe4C&pg=PA404|title=Endocrine System Diseases: New Insights for the Healthcare Professional: 2013 Edition|date=22 July 2013|publisher=ScholarlyEditions|isbn=978-1-4816-5848-5|p=404|ref={{sfnref|Endocrine System Diseases: New Insights for the Healthcare Professional|2013}}}}\n* {{citation |author1=Zohra Zaidi|author2=S.W Lanigan|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=I0GFGJfVeFIC&pg=PR10|title=Dermatology in Clinical Practice|date=10 March 2010|publisher=Springer Science & Business Media|isbn=978-1-84882-862-9|p=x|ref={{sfnref|Zohra Zaidi|S.W Lanigan|2010}}}}\n* {{citation |author1=Mohammad Aslam Uqaili|author2=Khanji Harijan|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=rndnOvfTDW4C&pg=PA259|title=Energy, Environment and Sustainable Development|date=14 October 2011|publisher=Springer Science & Business Media|isbn=978-3-7091-0109-4|p=259|ref={{sfnref|Mohammad Aslam Uqaili|Khanji Harijan|2011}}}}\n* {{citation |author=Renaux, Helen|title=True Children of the Raj|year=2011|publisher=Trafford Publishing|isbn=978-1-4669-0177-3|p=159|